  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this case control study is to explore the possible association between periodontal
      destruction and serum anti-CCP antibodies in RA patients and healthy subjects.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      In patients with RA, the anti-CCP antibody titer seems positively correlated to their
      periodontal destruction and disease activity in comparison with healthy subjects.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
